rows.label: qst103901_msg0002
rows.name: You take good care of us.

rows.label: qst103901_msg0003
rows.name:
Huh? Are you sure it wasn't
closer to 90,000G?

rows.label: qst103901_msg0005
rows.name:
But that's about 30,000G short!
Maybe some of the money was stolen
on the way?

rows.label: qst103901_msg0006
rows.name: Dearie me, do you really think so?

rows.label: qst103901_msg0007
rows.name:
I did think it seemed like a
strange amount...

rows.label: qst103901_msg0010
rows.name:
And when I sent you that Cloud Sea
Braised Shark, the handling fee
was simply enormous.

rows.label: qst103901_msg0009
rows.name:
We should go check with Maxim
the courier in Avaritia.
